	      <h1 class="w3-text-teal">Ultralight Backpacking - The Big Three</h1>
	      <p>A heavy pack can make backpacking a burden instead of an adventure. Lightening your backpacking kit can have drastic effects on your daily milage and physical exertion. The Big Three are your three main pieces of gear, which include shelter, sleeping system, and backpack. These items make up the majority of pack weight and are usually the most glaring overweight pieces of gear. The following is a guide to lighten your backpacking gear, focusing on The Big Three.</p>
	    
	  </div>
